summary: An Ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 5001, entitled "An Ordinance regulating the use of sidewalks by merchants and tradesmen in front of their places of business in the City of Seattle, and providing a penalty fore any violation of the same", and Ordinance No. 14032, entitled "An Ordinance amending Ordinance No. 5001, entitled "An Ordinance regulating the use of sidewalks by merchants and tradesmen in front of their places of business in the City of Seattle, and providing a penalty for any violation of the same".
